Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Opening}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.85,0:00:07.69,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Faint-hearted traveler, you should pull back now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.69,0:00:11.40,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Before you collapse
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.40,0:00:15.16,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}But you still say that you want to go on?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.16,0:00:21.91,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}To the other side of the distant sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.80,0:00:41.35,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Thousands of travelers have prayed to me before
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.35,0:00:48.86,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}After they collapsed at the other end of their journey
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.86,0:00:56.53,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}In a place that is not here, in a time that is not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.53,0:01:04.75,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}You're searching, saying that there's love there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.75,0:01:12.26,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Even though you could just patiently wait
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.26,0:01:17.47,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}For the destiny that I have given you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.47,0:01:22.35,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Do you know I'm a Venus?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.18,0:01:26.94,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Faint-hearted traveler, come closer to me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.94,0:01:30.82,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}Come sit at my feet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.82,0:01:34.49,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}I will embrace you and show you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:38.32,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}What is waiting beyond the distant sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.32,0:01:44.33,KaraokeT,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}What you wanna go high? Make it heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.04,0:01:51.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.48,0:01:57.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Our country's first manned exploratory\Nspace rocket, the Lion, was launched.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.41,0:02:04.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}However, 72 seconds after liftoff,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.08,0:02:07.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the liquid fuel booster suddenly exploded,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.17,0:02:12.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and although the Space Control Center\Nactivated its self-destruct system,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.90,0:02:16.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the flight suspension system did not function correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.93,0:02:24.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Lion fell into an urban area and caused a\Nhuge disaster with many civilian casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.89,0:02:27.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Five years later...
