Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:35.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.07,0:03:38.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asumi, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.78,0:03:48.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, I'm Suzunari, Asumi-chan's\Nteacher at Yuigahama Elementary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.91,0:03:51.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My condolences on your recent loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.54,0:03:53.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:56.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei, have you seen Asumi around?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.13,0:03:57.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:04:00.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Has something happened to Asumi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.63,0:04:04.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, she took the cremated ashes\Nand went off somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:05.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.54,0:04:34.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't see it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.52,0:04:56.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey mister, what's your job?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:05:00.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An advertising mascot?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.07,0:05:02.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or maybe someone from the circus?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.15,0:05:06.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You... You can tell who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.74,0:05:09.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know, so that's why I'm asking!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.37,0:05:10.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now this is surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.79,0:05:13.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can see me, little one?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.29,0:05:15.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it strange for me to see you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.21,0:05:18.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I am a ghost, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:22.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.17,0:05:23.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a strange old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:24.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.26,0:05:27.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, don't call me old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.34,0:05:29.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if I look like this, I'm still young and strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:32.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This T-shirt shows my fashion sense, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.56,0:05:33.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.10,0:05:37.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, why are you wearing that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.65,0:05:39.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of reasons behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.61,0:05:40.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me see your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.86,0:05:41.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.15,0:05:44.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Little one, what is that box that you're carrying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.53,0:05:47.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This? Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.99,0:05:48.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:49.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:51.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asumi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:56.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So this is where you went.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.37,0:05:59.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Suzunari-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:01.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your father is looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:03.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.05,0:06:03.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.22,0:06:10.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, will you be here tomorrow too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:10.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.97,0:06:13.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Great! Bye-bye, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:15.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there someone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:16.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.39,0:06:19.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't ask for your name!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.10,0:06:21.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name? Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:23.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can just call me Lion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:26.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lion-san? What a weird name!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:28.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.82,0:06:33.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wa... Asumi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.54,0:06:39.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who was she talking with?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.30,0:06:49.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asumi-chan, were you\Nwith someone back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:51.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.22,0:06:53.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He had a strange-looking lion head!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.72,0:06:55.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said he was a ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:06:58.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lion? A ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.77,0:07:02.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sometimes I just can't seem\Nto keep up with this girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:12.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Suzun{\i1}ari-sensei, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.74,0:07:15.24,Mourning,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\blur0.6\c&H16150E&\b1\4a&HFF&\pos(429.14,91.95)\org(429.14,91.95)\frz0.08\fax0.01\clip(m 368 70.22 l 489.78 69.33 490.67 96.89 367.11 96.89)\frx25.42\fry359.2}Kamogawa
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.21,0:07:26.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Truly, my condolences on your recent loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:30.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for causing so\Nmuch trouble today, sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.01,0:07:34.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Asumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.89,0:07:40.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you that this was something\Nvery important, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.39,0:07:43.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These ashes aren't a toy to be played with!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.15,0:07:47.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you listening Asumi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:50.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:56.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess being a single father is just no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.62,0:07:59.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She doesn't listen to a thing I say...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:00.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.91,0:08:03.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She may not truly feel that\Nher mother has passed away
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.46,0:08:08.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because when Asumi became old\Nenough to be aware of things,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:10.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,my wife was already in that state.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.17,0:08:13.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had to raise my daughter\Nwithout her knowing her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.80,0:08:17.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. It's rude of me to ask,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.10,0:08:19.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but what kind of person was your wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:21.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you remember it as well, sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.27,0:08:25.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rocket explosion incident five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:30.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My wife was a victim of that incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:32.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asumi was still only one year old.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:36.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My wife received grave\Nwounds on her face and head.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.74,0:08:39.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She ended up all bound up in a vegetative state.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.41,0:08:45.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the end, she passed away without regaining\Nconsciousness even once in those five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:50.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asumi once said that she'd like to be\Nable to see her mother just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:51.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.80,0:08:56.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, she had never seen her\Nmother's face, except in pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.43,0:08:58.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But ever since that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:02.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asumi hasn't spoken once\Nabout her mother again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:04.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.23,0:09:09.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What Asumi was thinking, how she felt...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.73,0:09:11.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:17.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So all that has happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.62,0:09:23.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:33.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your mother became a star too,\Ndidn't she, Asumi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:34.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A star?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:37.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. That's what I think happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.94,0:09:50.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A star, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:06.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Little one, you came to see me again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.91,0:10:08.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about school?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.54,0:10:10.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's summer vacation right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.42,0:10:11.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.92,0:10:14.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You seem to have a lot of\Nfree time yourself, Lion-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.13,0:10:17.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is school fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.97,0:10:19.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.47,0:10:23.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is Suzunari-sensei nice to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.22,0:10:27.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Lion-san, do you know Suzunari-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.48,0:10:28.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.81,0:10:30.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I happened to see her yesterday, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.77,0:10:32.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei is very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.94,0:10:35.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.15,0:10:37.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sometimes she gets a lonely expression...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.45,0:10:40.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A very lonely expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.87,0:10:51.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.43,0:11:00.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yuuko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.14,0:11:03.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good day!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.64,0:11:06.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The stairs here are so long\Nthey really take their toll on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.77,0:11:07.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
