Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.02,0:11:16.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My silly son must be pretty happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:18.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Every year at Obon,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.99,0:11:22.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he has such a pretty woman come visit him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.62,0:11:23.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.16,0:11:30.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, today is the day of the\NYuigahama fireworks display, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.29,0:11:34.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That boy wrote in a composition\Nin elementary school
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.54,0:11:39.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that his dream was to watch\Nfireworks from space.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:42.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Afterwards I heard from someone else that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.55,0:11:46.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,fireworks are too small to be seen from space.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.22,0:11:48.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you think about it, it's pretty obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:53.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But without even realizing that,\Nthat boy went on to be an astronaut...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:54.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He really was a silly boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.73,0:11:59.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's already been five years since then, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.19,0:12:02.70,Mourning,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\fs25\bord0\c&H292B25&\4a&HFF&\pos(558.67,298)\frx2\fry348}Takano Family
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.16,0:12:06.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shall we get going, Lion-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:08.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll help me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.41,0:12:11.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.01,0:12:24.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Already five years since then, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.01,0:12:25.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:44.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.03,0:12:45.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.53,0:12:49.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a figure of the Lion's mascot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:51.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can have it, Yuuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:55.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just a little trinket they sell at the\Nspace center's gift shop, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.46,0:12:57.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What, just a trinket, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.58,0:12:59.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.21,0:13:02.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess it'll make a good memento, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.05,0:13:04.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be saying things like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.38,0:13:07.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To someone who's going up soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.34,0:13:10.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just kidding! I'm really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.76,0:13:13.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really do get carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.94,0:13:17.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just one week left, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:19.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's pretty amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.57,0:13:21.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The youngest astronaut ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.61,0:13:25.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yuuko...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.03,0:13:31.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After I get back from this flight safely...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:32.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.91,0:13:34.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, I'd like for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:36.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.17,0:13:39.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no, that's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.96,0:13:41.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.05,0:13:43.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? Now you've got me wondering!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:45.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.88,0:13:47.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you after I get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.34,0:13:48.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.59,0:13:50.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.68,0:13:52.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure to tell you when I get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.64,0:13:54.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No good, it has to be now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.40,0:14:06.45,Bus Stop,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HAFA9A8&\pos(769.15,430.66)\blur0.63\org(769.15,430.66)\fry-3.2\frx2.76\frz2.68\fax-0.02\clip(m 704 378.67 l 834 371.33 836 434.67 704.67 440.67)}To\NYuigahama
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.40,0:14:06.45,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(680,241.714)\3c&HCAC5C6&\bord0\c&H2A327F&\blur0.6\org(680,241.714)\fry-12.38\frx2.58\frz4.28\fax-0.05\fnSquare721 BT}Bus\NStop
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:04.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why in the world did I say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:06.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A memento...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.95,0:14:11.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was a pretty bad joke, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.66,0:14:17.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.21,0:14:20.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, Asumi-chan's father?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:25.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? Asumi-chan took the\Nashes and disappeared again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.42,0:14:30.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, little one!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:33.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.43,0:14:35.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.56,0:14:36.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.81,0:14:39.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lion-san, you're supposed to\Nbe younger than you look!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.52,0:14:40.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a wimp!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.77,0:14:45.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These remains are as heavy\Nas a person to my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.69,0:14:48.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Talking nonsense like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:50.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But do you want to rest for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.41,0:14:52.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lion-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:55.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you play that thing from yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.04,0:14:56.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, gladly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:31.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Little one, did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.62,0:15:39.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Out of all the instruments, the harmonica\Nwas the first one to fly into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.04,0:15:41.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Space?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.21,0:15:47.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. In 1965, the pilot of the\NAmerican capsule, Gemini VI,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.42,0:15:50.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,wore a 3cm wide harmonica around\Nhis neck when he went up into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.38,0:15:55.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then he sent a present of\Nmusic down to Earth from space.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.68,0:15:59.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lion-san, you sure know a lot about space.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.52,0:16:00.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you ever been there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:03.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.90,0:16:08.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the Earth must be really\Npretty when you see it from space.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.69,0:16:13.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll never be able to see it since\NI ended up like this, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.49,0:16:17.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lion-san, could you really be a ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.20,0:16:20.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just once would have been fine,\Nbut I sure wanted to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:26.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asumi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:30.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asumi-chan! Answer me if you're there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.68,0:16:41.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just a little further!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.87,0:17:06.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it! There's a great view of it from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.55,0:17:14.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, this is Suzunari.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:17.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She doesn't seem to be out\Nhere by the shore either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.47,0:17:21.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought she might have come to the\Nbooths down here, so I asked around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:23.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But no one said that they had seen Asumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.02,0:17:27.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'll look around here one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.69,0:17:28.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:45.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Mom will be happy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.04,0:17:46.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm sure she will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.79,0:17:47.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.67,0:17:48.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.21,0:17:52.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you for helping me, Lion-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.30,0:17:56.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Little one, I have a favor to ask of you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.84,0:17:58.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could I ask you for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.59,0:18:00.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah! That's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.02,0:18:08.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, where did you go, Asumi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:12.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He had a strange-looking lion head!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.44,0:18:14.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:15.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A kidnapping?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.07,0:18:21.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Really... where could she have wandered off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.49,0:18:27.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe I should contact the police now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.50,0:18:35.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.76,0:18:39.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The door was locked, so I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.72,0:18:44.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you understand why I hit you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.77,0:18:49.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I told you already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.19,0:18:53.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not a toy, it's something very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.32,0:18:57.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And yet you still keep running off with it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.82,0:18:59.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those ashes are...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.20,0:19:00.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.49,0:19:03.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're the ashes of my\Nmother who gave birth to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.99,0:19:06.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you understand that, then why...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.91,0:19:08.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where did you take them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.16,0:19:13.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I buried them in the place with the\Nprettiest view of the Yuigahama Bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.96,0:19:15.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:17.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She seemed so lonely!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.72,0:19:23.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Closed up in that dark hospital room...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.14,0:19:26.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom always seemed so lonely in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.81,0:19:30.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then she got put in a little box when she died...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.98,0:19:33.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I felt so sorry for Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.57,0:19:37.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said it yourself, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.40,0:19:42.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said Mom always loved the\NYuigahama Bay, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.45,0:19:45.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.75,0:19:51.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.21,0:19:55.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was Mom happy to see the ocean again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.76,0:20:08.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These stairs are so long, geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.73,0:20:13.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:16.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? You found her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.61,0:20:18.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You found Asumi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.36,0:20:20.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.40,0:20:23.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry to have worried you, sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.66,0:20:27.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, and Asumi said that she\Nhad something to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:29.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello, sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.95,0:20:31.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.91,0:20:33.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.25,0:20:36.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei, do you know Lion-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.63,0:20:40.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lion-san said that he had something\Nhe wanted me to tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.80,0:20:43.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.18,0:20:44.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.14,0:20:49.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Don't be too mean to the Lion doll, Yuuko."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.18,0:20:53.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.02,0:20:54.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See ya, sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.48,0:20:56.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on! Asumi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.77,0:21:02.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's the only one who knows about this doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.02,0:21:32.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yuuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.52,0:21:36.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takano-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.05,0:22:06.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After I get back from this flight\Nsafely, I'd like for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.39,0:22:09.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.35,0:22:18.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's mean, going and\Nbecoming a star by yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.65,0:22:22.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Takano-kun, that's mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.32,0:22:31.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lion-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.87,0:22:34.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lion-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.54,0:22:37.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's not here today...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.75,0:22:42.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you fly to space on a rocket, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.54,0:22:46.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I grow up, I'm going to be a rocket pilot!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.63,0:22:49.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I'll let you ride for free, Lion-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.01,0:22:53.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So let me hear lots more stories!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.89,0:22:55.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lion-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.02,0:22:58.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Ending}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.69,0:23:11.36,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}Look up at the stars in the night
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.70,0:23:23.92,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}The little stars, with their little lights
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.92,0:23:37.22,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}Are singing of humble happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.22,0:23:50.78,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}Look up at the stars in the night
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.78,0:24:03.75,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}Just like us, the stars without names
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.75,0:24:20.27,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur2}Are praying for humble happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.99,0:24:34.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Preview}
