Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.16,0:24:36.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Winter of the third year of middle school...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.03,0:24:38.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We have to be deciding our futures now,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.74,0:24:40.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I'm still not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.75,0:24:45.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to attend Tokyo Space University\Nand learn to be an astronaut
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.29,0:24:47.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I'm sure that my dad will be against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.46,0:24:53.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And it takes lots of money, so I think that\Nmaybe I should give up on that dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.76,0:24:57.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next time on Twin Spica:\NAsumi's Dream.
